Lamp Soup

Ingredients:
    [list]
    [*]Water 1.20lt
    [*]Lamb Head x1
    [*]Onion x1
    [*]Meat Broth 0.15 lt
    [*]Tomato Paste 200g
    [*]Red Pepper x1
    [*]Flour 400g
    [/list]
Steps:
    Slice
        Onion x1
        Red Pepper x1

    Add to a Cookpot and Boil
        Water 1.20lt
        Onion Slices
        Red Pepper Slices
        Flour 400g
        Tomato Paste 200g
        Lamb Head
        Meat Broth 0.15lt

    Transfer to Bowl
        Mixture 0.20 lt

    Serve Hot